message.content: {"scores":{"l":5,"v":5,"u":5,"s":5,"p":5,"t":5},"justification":"The lesson plan titled 'The End of Roman Britain' for Key Stage 1 history is fully compliant across all categories. The lesson avoids upsetting, sensitive, or distressing content and does not include any nudity or sexual content. Physical activities or exploration involving safety concerns are not present, nor is there any external content requiring adult supervision. Finally, the lesson does not contain any toxic content such as guides to self-harm or illegal activities.
